Package com.game.Utilities

Class AssetSetter

java.lang.Object
com.game.Utilities.AssetSetter
public class AssetSetter extends Object
Responsible for setting and positioning items in the game world.

This class initializes game items, such as beds, papers, coffee, books, and vortexes, and assigns them to specific positions within the game environment. It is used to populate the game world with interactive and collectible items that the player can interact with or collect during gameplay.
